Class RemoteEntity

  • java.lang.Object
    • tk.michaelmckey.microcontrollerremote.db.entity.RemoteEntity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RecyclerElement

    public class RemoteEntity
extends java.lang.Object
implements RecyclerElement
    Stores the title, layout type, connection method, connection info and the time of creation for a given RemoteEntity
    Version:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Michael McKey
